    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>A Grievous Wrong to Mothers, Children, and Society</strong>&mdash;There are parents who, without consideration as to whether or not they can do justice to a large family, fill their houses with these helpless little beings, who are wholly dependent upon their parents for care and instruction.... This is a grievous wrong, not only to the mother, but to her children and to society....",
