    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Other Factors to Be Considered</strong>&mdash;God would have parents act as rational beings and live in such a manner that each child may be properly educated, that the mother may have strength and time to employ her mental powers in disciplining her little ones for the society of the angels. She should have courage to act nobly her part and to do her work in the fear and love of God, that her children may prove a blessing to the family and to society.",
