    "content": "<strong>Counsel to Parents of a Large Family</strong>&mdash;The question to be settled by you is, &ldquo;Am I raising a family of children to strengthen the influence and swell the ranks of the powers of darkness, or am I bringing up children for Christ?&rdquo;",
